==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Flagging
<hw>Flag"ging</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A pavement or
sidewalk of flagstones; flagstones, collectively.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Flagging</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Flagging
<hw>Flag"ging</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Growing languid, weak, or
spiritless; weakening; delaying.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Flag"ging*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Flaggy</ent>⟦br⟧
